<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<html xmlns:MadCap="http://www.madcapsoftware.com/Schemas/MadCap.xsd">
    <body>
        <p><b>To hide a document:</b>
        </p>
        <p>When you hover your cursor over a document, the <b>visibility</b> icon (<img src="../Images/icon-visibility-visible.png" style="vertical-align: text-bottom;" />) is displayed. Select <b>visibility</b>  (<img src="../Images/icon-visibility-visible.png" style="vertical-align: text-bottom;" />)  to display the visibility pop-up.</p>
        <p>You can view the document's  visibility conditions  (if available) at the  pop-up. Select <b>Hide</b> to hide the document.</p>
    </body>
</html>